item.title: goals for this blog
item.description: Write something once a week. I have a lot I want to talk about… my experience with swimming, my work, and just things I find interesting. Some series that I hope to write in the coming weeks include: Reflections on swimming My current work in ML Hobbies i.e. muay thai, jiu jitsu Things that I want to learn more about, i.e. restorative agriculture
